data.meta_description: Gay Actors - Free download as Word Doc (.doc / .docx), PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. This document provides brief biographies of 33 gay actors. It includes their name, notable roles, date and place of birth, and some biographical details. The actors range from established stars like Matt Bomer, Neil Patrick Harris, and Rupert Everett to up-and-coming actors like Max Jenkins, Matthew Wilkas, and Murray Bartlett. Overall, the document highlights the accomplishments and career trajectories of a diverse group of openly gay men in the film and television industry.
